dpo@demandbase.com
.
Demandbase has appointed an EU Representative to act on our behalf and serve as a direct contact for supervisory authorities and individuals in the European Union. If you are in the EU or EEA and would like to contact our EU Representative, please email:
GDPRrepresentative@demandbase.com
.
