Residents of U.S. States other than California
Certain other U.S. states have enacted laws similar in nature to the CCPA.  Those laws exclude certain Personal Data, such as the types of Personal Data we collect, use, and disclose, from their scope.
However, we will honor “requests to know,” “requests to delete,” or “requests to correct” made by any individual in the United States, other than Personal Data about job applications or employment with us.  To make a “request to know,” “request to delete,” or “request to correct” your Personal Data, send us an email at
